name: CosmoNutz
summary:
Help Kosmo wipe the Geloidz from the face of the planet in this awesome Sokoban puzzle game!
Quite unbelievably, those dastardly Geloidz have been at it again! They've only gone and impounded Kosmo's shiny Rocket for landing on the Royal lawns – how was he to know an icky swamp was a Royal lawn anyway?
